cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.DS 

The paper deals with clustering of data sets containing both text content and connection structure. This can be applied to various fields such as information retrieval (cs.IR), social networks (cs.SI), machine learning (cs.LG), data mining (cs.SD), and data structures (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
